Type: Package
Package: yamlcv
Title: Generate Beautiful CVs from 'yaml' Files
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stefan",
           family = "Fleck",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stefan.b.fleck@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3344-9851"))
Maintainer: Stefan Fleck <stefan.b.fleck@gmail.com>
Description: Generate beautiful CVs from 'yaml' files. Currently
    only supports generating pdf CVs based on posquit0's Awesome-CV
    (https://github.com/posquit0/Awesome-CV) latex template, but in theory
    more templates and output formats could be supported.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/s-fleck/yamlcv
BugReports: https://github.com/s-fleck/yamlcv/issues
