    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
    commonmark (>= 1.7),
    knitr (>= 1.30),
    tinytex (>= 0.27),
    withr (>= 2.3.0),
    yaml (>= 2.2.1)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.3.2)
Encoding: UTF-8
